@startuml
hide empty description

title PhotographerDelivery State Machine

[*] --> Registered

Registered --> Discovering : startDiscovery()
Discovering --> Discovered : discoverySucceeded(sourceManifest)
Discovering --> Failed : discoveryFailed(reason)

Discovered --> Importing : startImport()
Importing --> Imported : importSucceeded(importSummary)
Importing --> Failed : importFailed(reason)

Imported --> ReviewReady : createInitialReviewRun()
ReviewReady --> Archived : archiveDelivery()

Failed --> Registered : retryAfterFix()

note right of Discovering
Source is an ingest reference
(e.g., Google Photos shared link).
It is not the canonical runtime URL.
end note

note right of Imported
Canonical runtime image URLs are hosted
on the AfricaStage/OTW ImageServer.
end note

@enduml
